<head>
		
	<texsetting wysiwyg="0"/><paper pagenumber="1" margin="20,20,20,25">A4</paper></head><body fontsize="12pt" fontface="ＭＳ Ｐ明朝">
<p><mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>が急現象関数であるというのは、</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>が何回でも微分できる</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsup"><munit italic="1">l</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi<mlink type="rsup"><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>は各整数<mblock><munit italic="1">l</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit entity="1">geq</munit><munit>0</munit></mblock>について常に有界</p>
<p/>
<p>という性質を持つ関数である。例えば<mblock><munit italic="1">e<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit></mblock>は急減少関数である。今<mblock><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">infty</munit><munit>&lt;</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>&lt;</munit><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mblock>において区分的に連続な関数</p>
<p>からなる列</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit></mblock></p>
<p>がどんな関数<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>についても有限な積分値<mblock><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink><mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit> </munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit><munit>,</munit><munit>2</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>を持つとする。さらにどんな<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>に対しても</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">lim<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">rightarrow</munit><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink><mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit></mblock></p>
<p>が存在するならば、この値を<mblock><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>と書き、<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit></mblock>から<mblock><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>への対応を表す汎関数<mblock><munit italic="1">u</munit></mblock>を超関数と呼ぶ。これを</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink><mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">lim<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">rightarrow</munit><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink><mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">varphi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit></mblock></p>
<p>と表現する。</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>として<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">upsilon<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit><munit>/</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>をとれば、<mblock><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>は<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">delta</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>である。</p></body></InftyDocument>
